`sports` | `health_beauty` | `entertainment` | `home_services` | `education` | `events`

## Rank vs Subscription (They are SEPARATE systems)

- **Subscription Tiers** (paid): Free / Premium / VIP
- **Ranks** (earned): Newbie / Regular / Pro / Pasha
